verbose_text: By analyzing the expression of CXCR2 in ovarian cancer using Kaplan-Meier Plotter (ovarian cancer) (http://kmplot.com/analysis/index.php?p=service&cancer=ovar), we found that the high expression of CXCR2 was significantly correlated with lower progression-free survival (PFS) (P = 0.049) and post-progression survival (PPS) (P = 0.015) but not overall survival (OS) (P = 0.21) in ovarian cancer.
